convention card about non-alertable bids is considered to be
&quot;disclosed&quot;. If you regularly include wild distributions in your
strong frocing opener the phrase &quot;UNB NonDef OK&quot; or &quot;Light w/ Wild
Dist&quot; (or whatever your agreement really is) will win you the
argument, if the director is called.
